WEBVTT

00:02.480 --> 00:04.100
Eight years ago,
I was lead prosecutor

00:04.100 --> 00:05.980
on a murder trial
that divided the country.

00:05.980 --> 00:08.350
When the jury found movie star
Sevvy Johnson

00:08.350 --> 00:10.440
not guilty of double homicide,

00:10.440 --> 00:11.640
I was devastated.

00:11.640 --> 00:12.850
You did everything
you could, Maya.

00:12.850 --> 00:14.190
I walked out of the courtroom

00:14.190 --> 00:16.810
and left that life
and everyone in it behind.

00:16.810 --> 00:18.600
But then the unthinkable
happened.

00:18.600 --> 00:19.600
He killed again.

00:19.600 --> 00:20.850
You have to come back, Maya.

00:20.850 --> 00:22.310
This time, we're gonna get him.

00:22.310 --> 00:24.850
I can't go back to jail.
You won't.

00:24.850 --> 00:27.350
The police know
who the killer is...

00:27.350 --> 00:29.440
Ben Mitchell.
Being back is complicated.

00:29.440 --> 00:30.520
You're supposed to be
ride or die.

00:30.520 --> 00:32.100
I didn't even know
where you'd gone.

00:32.100 --> 00:33.350
Nothing and no one
is the same...

00:33.350 --> 00:35.440
You got married.
Yeah.

00:35.440 --> 00:36.480
Including me.

00:36.480 --> 00:38.060
She's been through a lot.
So have you,

00:38.060 --> 00:40.020
but you stayed when she ran.

00:40.020 --> 00:41.140
The evidence is there.

00:41.140 --> 00:42.400
We just need to find it.

00:42.400 --> 00:44.440
He did it again.
He gave me this.

00:44.440 --> 00:46.810
I am lead on this case.
Maya's staying.

00:46.810 --> 00:48.770
I'm making her
the lead prosecutor.

00:48.770 --> 00:49.900
I just heard from my guy
on the inside.

00:49.900 --> 00:50.900
They got a search warrant.

00:50.900 --> 00:52.440
I owe you one.

00:52.440 --> 00:55.560
But I need you
to get rid of this now.

00:55.560 --> 00:57.310
This time,
he's not gonna get away with it.

00:57.310 --> 00:59.020
I'm gonna get justice.

